track.name: Don't Explain
comments: BEAUTIFUL MS SIMONE, YOU CAN FEEL HER WHEN SHE SINGS
Very haunting rendition! Even more so than Lady Day's
A heartbreaking version of this song.
What a great voice! One of the best!
Gut-wrenchingly beautiful. And as much of a Billie fan as I am, I like this version better.

this is fuckin' great!!
sweet and expressive
I've never heard anything better than this - NEVER!
Something from the deep inside of a woman's soul...
